media:group.media:title: Khan Stories: Mr. Brown
media:group.media:description:
Listen to how Scott Brown, a math teacher in Oregon, used Khan Academy to supercharge his classroom and help his students get the learning outcomes they were looking for. 

Mr. Brown teaches in a small school, but Khan Academy can help students in large school districts all over the United States achieve learning results and boost their test scores.

For more information, visit:  districts.khanacademy.org
